---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About MailPilot"
  description="Why MailPilot exists and how we review email marketing tools."
>
  <h1>About MailPilot</h1>
  <p>MailPilot is an independent review site for small businesses comparing email marketing platforms. We don't take sponsored reviews, and affiliate commissions never change our recommendations.</p>

  <h2>Who runs this</h2>
  <p>A small team of email marketers who got tired of the same recycled "Top 10" lists that read like they were written by someone who never logged into the tools. Every review here is based on actual usage and real pricing, not on what the vendor's homepage claims.</p>

  <h2>What we test</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Pricing across free, starter, and growth tiers — including hidden contact limits</li>
    <li>Ease of setup for a non-technical small business owner</li>
    <li>Automation features at each price point</li>
    <li>Deliverability on shared hosting IPs vs. dedicated IPs</li>
    <li>Real customer support response times</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we don't do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>We don't accept payment to write a review</li>
    <li>We don't bury the cons at the bottom of a 3,000-word review</li>
    <li>We don't recommend tools we haven't actually used</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>